Name: Secure the Skies
About the game: Secure the Skies is a music-based aerial combat game. The objective is to shoot out musical patterns to trap your opponent before they do the same. This game contains: -9 Musical Ships -9 Unique Arenas -Single-Player Mode -Local Split-screen Multiplayer -Online 1v1 Multiplayer
